overview: When witches Riley & Emily start terrorizing their classmates, student / paranormal investigator Kristen Scott is called in to stop them. Armed with a cross, holy water, and a circle of salt, Kristen tries to take on the demons that the witches summon but struggles. To put an end to it, she's going to have to go into the witches den, but what will it take to stop them?
title: Paranormal
